title: Angels score 5 in 9th, beat Rangers 11-10
text:
> Texas Angels score 5 in 9th, beat Rangers 11-10 Los Angeles Angels' Johnny Giavotella is congratulated in the dugout by teammates during the ninth inning of a baseball game against the Texas Rangers in Arlington, Texas, Saturday, Oct. 3, 2015. Giovatella hit an RBI single scoring Drew Stubbs in the night inning, leading the Angels to an 11-10 win. (AP Photo/LM Otero)
